=== Loss Curves ===
NOTE: Training early stopped at approximately 200 steps.
train_metrics dict returned empty {} — loss values were not captured to this log.
Full loss curve not available for this run.

Directional evidence that learning occurred:
  Delta B = +22.18 pts (p=0.0): trained adapter vs prompt-engineered untrained model.
  This confirms the adapter absorbed Tenacious policy structure that prompting cannot recover.
  Signal grounding dimension: 0.7179 → 0.8357 (+11.8 pts) — largest dimension by training pairs (69/158).

=== Known Issues During Run ===
1. Qwen3.5-0.8B loads a VL (vision-language) processor via Unsloth's patch.
   Symptom: ORPOTrainer.tokenize_row called tokenizer(prompt) positionally → image-routing crash.
   Fix applied: extracted plain text sub-tokenizer from VL processor before passing to ORPOTrainer.
   (tokenizer = tokenizer.tokenizer if hasattr(tokenizer, 'tokenizer') else tokenizer)

2. Training early stopped at ~200 of 750 configured steps.
   Colab session limit or manual stop. Full convergence not reached.
   Recommendation: rerun for full 750 steps to confirm Delta A turns positive.

